title: Elder Scrolls Online Beta (November 21, 2013)
description:
This is the beta version of ESO, an upcoming MMORPG by the makers of skyrim.

This download includes an installer for the games beta launcher. From there the game will download and install. Total size when installed is about 27 GB.

YOU MUST HAVE A BETA ACCOUNT TO PLAY, [u]BUT I WILL BE FOCUSING ALL OF MY EFFORTS TO MAKING A WORKAROUND/CRACK FOR THIS!

For now you can download this, install the latest version, and either us a beta account you may have, or wait for a crack.

Happy Gaming!
